{"tid":857633,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[重推] 巴絲打Board Game 活動","createTime":"2018-10-11T08:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T06:57:30.000Z","uid":62225,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9c61aa04e6a930807435e9809a977e87f5e72a72","tid":857633,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:28:26.000Z","msg":"以前我地有一個月一次玩board game連登仔活動，最後幾個月都無搞到lu。今個月搞番！！<br />\n<br />\n暑假個陣搞左個細細地既Board Game 比賽，黎玩既連登巴絲都應該玩得幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次我地從新黎過搵番多d 未認識既，希望有興趣既巴絲打有興趣就黎玩。<br />\n<br />\n報名link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/zGNjL75AoycrC2iv2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FzGNjL75AoycrC2iv2&d=pWbpC%2BUQwT7NA%2FgVgW1ezwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b7562d6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/zGNjL75AoycrC2iv2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：毒然活動"},{"pid":"3213e720619b7e8cccbe117af6590c892613f107","tid":857633,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T09:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550ea289a4415693325c3fcd2c42062c4c08f6e0","tid":857633,"uid":65220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T11:30:35.000Z","msg":"玩啲咩"},{"pid":"c124c71fa9b4baf1104d73dcae9505b5b159cb90","tid":857633,"uid":62225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"550ea289a4415693325c3fcd2c42062c4c08f6e0","tid":857633,"uid":65220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T11:30:35.000Z","msg":"玩啲咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T11:33:04.000Z","msg":"之前玩過好多款ga la. 都係一d 5~8 個人都玩到既桌遊。主要都會係容易將唔識既人放埋一齊都會玩得開心既game. 有時仲需要多d 溝通元素，方便毒巴絲可以同唔同既人互動下。<br />\n<br />\n今次玩咩就。。。你黎咪知law"},{"pid":"0513095c06bda8eabe30358201a216f26f241d04","tid":857633,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike